    {
      "id": "insight:e6dfdf7fd7795bfc",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "In the end, the customer and the customer alone determines whether you win or lose.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.4
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:45ab02f3c96d4b78",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "In the end, the customer and the customer alone determines whether you win or lose.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 2258,
        "char_end": 2341,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 149000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 154000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - Scaling Global Organizations in _20260421-175429_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:1182bedddfe7dd41",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "And it's a very simple equation. If you keep them coming back, you've got a good chance. And if you don't, you lose.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 2342,
        "char_end": 2458,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 154000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 162000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - Scaling Global Organizations in _20260421-175429_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:8e542c9c8fe87aa2",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "So if you take care of your customer, you know who your customer is, and you give them what they want just the way they want it, no matter what business you're in, you've got a really good chance.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 3613,
        "char_end": 3809,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 237000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 250000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - Scaling Global Organizations in _20260421-175429_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:18d8c9f9301e1b35",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "I feel that I really get grounded with the customers and understanding what they're trying to accomplish and how I can help them.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 45795,
        "char_end": 45924,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 3134000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 3142000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - Scaling Global Organizations in _20260421-175429_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:5574a48e715fca0f",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "A lot of people talk about sales and the idea of running corporations. It's all based on the customer and the customer alone. They determine whether you win or lose.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 45925,
        "char_end": 46090,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 3143000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 3158000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - Scaling Global Organizations in _20260421-175429_8eb5f9d2.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:d4649faf17b7c6eb",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "If you take care of your customer, you know who your customer is, and you give them what they want just the way they want it, no matter what business you're in, you've got a really good chance.",
        "episode_id": "4255b42e-3a9e-11f1-8eee-179e850fd703",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.07
